Gina Malo https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gina_Malo 0 Gina Malo (June 1, 1909 – November 30, 1963) was an American film actress, born Janet Flynn in Cincinnati, Ohio. She appeared in a number of British films in the 1930s, often playing an American.
